quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  17,41,"Uye zvirokwazvo, takatsanangura (vimbiso neyeuchidzo nezviratidzo zvedu) muQur’aan iri kuti vangarangarire, asi hazvivawedzeri kusara kwekuramba"
  17,42,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Dai panga pane vamwe vanamwari pamwe naivo (Allah) sezvavanotaura, vangadai vakatsvaga nzira kuna Tenzi vechigaro (vachida kufarirwa nekuva pedyo navo).”"
  17,43,Kurumbidzwa kwese ndekwavo! Uye vari pamusoro-soro pezvakaipa zvavanotaura! (Kuti kune vamwe vanamwari pamwechete naAllah)
  17,44,"Matenga manomwe nepasi nezvese zviri imomo zvinovarumbidza, uye hapana chinhu asi chinorumbidza kukudzwa kwavo. Asi hamunzwi kurumbidza kwazvo. Zvirokwazvo, vane tsitsi zhinji, vanoregerera zvikuru"
  17,45,"Uye paunoverenga Qur’aan (Muhammad (SAW)), tinoisa pakati pako nepakati peavo vasingatendi muzuva rekupedzisira, chidziviso chakavanzika (kuti vasanzwe kana kurinzwisisa)"
  17,46,"Uye takava tinoputira moyo yavo kuti vasarinzwisise (Qur’aan), uye munzeve dzavo havanzwi. Uye kana ukataura Tenzi vako vega muQur’aan, vanofuratira kumashure kwavo nekusada"
  17,47,"Tinoziva zvakanyanya zvavanoteerera pavakunoteerera. Uye pavanotaurirana muchivande, vanoita zvakaipa vanoti: “Munotevera murume akaroiwa.”"
  17,48,"Tarisa mienzaniso yavanopa pamusoro pako. Naizvozvo vakarasika, uye havawani nzira"
  17,49,"Uye vanoti: “Kana tava mapfupa uye taparadzwa, tichava tinomutswa here sezvisikwa zvitsva?”"
  17,50,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Ivai matombo kana simbi.”"
  17,51,"“Kana chimwe chisikwa chakakura mumoyo yenyu (muchamutswa).” Naizvozvo vachati: “Ndiani achatidzorera (hupenyu)?” Iti: “Avo vakakusikai pakutanga!” Naizvozvo vachadzungudza misoro yavo kwauri vachiti: “Zvichaitika rinhi?” Iti: “Zvimwe manje manje!”"
  17,52,"Pazuva iro ravachakusheedzai, uye muchadavira nekurumbidzwa kwavo, uye muchafunga kuti makagara (pano panyika) kwenguva diki"